text: Barwell Athletic F.C. was an English association football club based in Barwell, England. ==History== The club entered the FA Cup on four occasions, but never went further than the 1st Qualifying Round.http://fchd.info/BARWELLA.HTM In 1992 they merged with Hinckley F.C. to form Barwell F.C.http://fchd.info/BARWELL.HTM ==References== Category:Defunct football clubs in England Category:Defunct football clubs in Leicestershire Category:Association football clubs disestablished in 1992
